abstract static class SQLXMLImpl.SAXDOMCommon<T extends Adjusting.XML.Parsing<T>> extends SQLXMLImpl.AdjustingJAXPParser<T>
Extends AdjustingJAXPParser with some of the older adjustments that can be made the same way for SAX and DOM (StAX should not extend this class, but just implement the adjustments its own different way).
